Refiloe Jane (a mụrụ n'abalị anọ nke n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1992) bụ onye egwuregwu bọọlụ South Africa nke na-agba bọọlụ dị ka onye ọnọ n'etiti
Ọ na-agbara AC Milan bọọlụ na Italian Serie A Women's League na nke otu ma ụmụ nwanyị South Afrika bu South Africa women's national team
Ọ gbaburu bọọlụ na Vaal University of Technology na Canberra United na W-League na Australia.
N'abalị iri abụọ nke ọnwa August afọ gị I 2018, Canberra United kwupụtara na ha bịanyere aka na nsonye Jane maka 2018-19 W-League Season
O sonyeere klọb ahụ ya na onye South Africa ibe ya bụ Rhoda Mulaudzi, ha bụ ndị egwuregwu mbụ si South Africa sonyere n'ọgbụgba W-League.

Mgbe ya na ndị otu Australia Canberra United kewara n'ọnwa Eprel afọ 2019, Refiloe bịanyere aka na Italian Serie A Women's League outfit AC Milan na nkwekọrịta otu afọ maka ego ụgwọ ọnwa na-akọwaghị ego ole ọ bụ.
Jane nọchitere anya South Africa na 2012 London Olympics N'ọnwa Septemba afọ 2014, a guzoro aha Jane  na ndepụta maka 2014 African Women's Championship na Namibia.
A kpọrọ Jane na ndị otu South Africa maka 2016 Summer Olympics
Ọ na-egwu nkeji ọ bụla n'ime egwuregwu atọ nke otu ahụ.
N'ọnwa Febụwarị 2019, Jane pụtara na mkpọputa Mpụta nke otu narị ugboro na South Africa.
Akara na nsonaazụ depụtara goolu South Africa na mbido ndị mbụ
